{"schema_version":"v1","message_id":"20260530T080417270320_handoff","session_id":"ses_188254686ffefEQuL3CuliZwBL","sender":"lane-owner","recipient":"orchestrator","kind":"handoff","wave":null,"subject":"Lane lifecycle-engine-integration complete — completed","body":"{\n  \"lane_id\": \"lifecycle-engine-integration\",\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"waves_completed\": [\"learning\", \"plan\", \"review\", \"execution\", \"validation\"],\n  \"repair_cycles\": 2,\n  \"files_created\": [\n    \"packages/opencode/src/lifecycle/definition.ts\",\n    \"packages/opencode/src/lifecycle/builtins.ts\",\n    \"packages/opencode/src/lifecycle/engine.ts\",\n    \"packages/opencode/src/lifecycle/loop.ts\",\n    \"packages/opencode/src/lifecycle/lifecycle.ts\"\n  ],\n  \"files_modified\": [],\n  \"verification\": { \"typecheck\": \"pass\" },\n  \"blockers\": [],\n  \"lessons\": [\n    \"Effect Schema APIs: Schema.Literals([...]) for enums, Schema.decodeUnknownOption for parsing unknown inputs\",\n    \"Layer-level ToolRegistry override can't shadow captured closures in prompt.ts — compositor uses prompt-based phase instructions instead\",\n    \"Log.create logger methods use object-style (message, {key: value}), not printf format strings\"\n  ],\n  \"recommendation\": \"merge\",\n  \"summary\": \"Created lifecycle package with 5 files. definition.ts provides PhaseDefinition, LifecycleDefinition, TransitionDefinition schemas with Effect Schema, plus parseLifecycle/getNextPhase helpers. builtins.ts provides CARTOGRAPHER_LIFECYCLE, EXECUTOR_LIFECYCLE, CRITIC_LIFECYCLE, LANE_OWNER_LIFECYCLE constants with per-phase allowedTools. engine.ts implements hook-based LifecycleEngine execute() supporting retry loops (maxRetries), escalation strategies (abort/skip/blocker), and DAG+linear phase transitions with getNextPhase. loop.ts provides runLifecycledPrompt compositor that wraps SessionPrompt.loop with lifecycle phase management — resolves lifecycle from agent config or BUILTIN_LIFECYCLES, passthrough for agents without lifecycle. All files pass typecheck (tsgo --noEmit) with zero errors across the package. No modifications to dirty files (prompt.ts, processor.ts, registry.ts remain untouched).\"\n}","sent_at":"2026-05-30T08:04:17.270526+00:00"}
